### CI Workflows and Quality Gates

- Gates to pass before merge:

```bash
make format
make lint
make type
make test
make docs
```

- Install pre-commit hooks locally:

```bash
pre-commit install --install-hooks
```

- Type baseline (do not increase errors): [mypy_baseline.json](mdc:mypy_baseline.json)

```bash
./scripts/dev.sh type-changed
./scripts/dev.sh type-baseline
./scripts/dev.sh type-baseline-update
```

- Workflows live in `.github/workflows/` (CI, style, fast, nightly, deprecations, eval, markdownlint, docker).

