### CI Gates

- `ci.yml`: matrix Python (3.10–3.12) → `make ci-all` + docs contract check.
- `ci-style.yml`: format-check, lint, guards.
- `ci-fast.yml`: `make ci-fast`; optional strict docs import.
- `ci-nightly.yml`: full `make ci-all` with ffmpeg & yt-dlp.
- `markdownlint.yml`: markdown style for `*.md`.
- `deprecations.yml`: scans and enforces upcoming deadlines.
- `eval.yml` / `golden.yml`: regression/eval harness.
- `docker.yml`: build/push image (tags and main/master).
